short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly switch between previous and current tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows you to easily and quickly switch between the previous tab you clicked on and your current tab.

To use it simply hit CTRL+Q, on macOs you can use CTRL+Q.
